body:
Expected no less- after seeing the cover and all.
Great work, you made a good H doujin while still maintaining the elements in which ai enma has, yes not a slut, but enjoyed it upon experiencing it for the first time, emotionless, not caring,. (well that was atleast in my perspective, since i can't read moonrunes) but still, Wow, i.... i mean, we need more doujins like of this caliber (at the very least), to be honest.
